    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Firmavimus nos
                        gloriosissima domna <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/2002"
                            >Scaniperga</persName> et domnus <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">
                            vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/374"
                            >Liudprand</persName>, summi <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducibus</rs> gentis
                        Longobardorum, per rogum <persName key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/2005"
                            >Eufimie</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatisse</rs> et, oratricis nostre, in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> beate <orgName
                                key="#Monasteries #Abbesses #Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1901">Sancte Marie</orgName> genitricis domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi, quod fundatum esse dinoscitur in locum, qui nominatur
                            <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/2301">Loco Sano</placeName>,
                        ubi <persName key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/2003">Albileopa</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> regimen tenere videtur, hoc est <rs
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >condoma</rs> nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Rodo">Rodone</name></persName> cum uxore, filios et
                        filias suas, vel cum integra eorum pertinencia; et condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Candolus">Candolus</name></persName> cum uxore, filios
                        et filias, vel cum omnia sua, qui habitare videntur in
                        <placeName key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Viviano</placeName>; et condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Maurus">Mauro</name></persName> cum uxore, filios et
                        filias seu germanos, vel cum omnia eorum pertinencia; condoma nomine
                            <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Ansualdus">Ansoald</name></persName> cum uxore, filios
                        et filias seu germanos, vel cum omnibus rebus eorum, qui habitare videntur
                        in <placeName key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Turri</placeName>; condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Maroaldus">Maroald</name></persName> cum uxore, filios
                        et filias, germanos seu nepote suo, vel cum omnia eorum pertinencia; condoma
                        nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Marullo">Marullo</name></persName> cum uxore, filios et
                        filias, seu germanos suos, vel cum omnia sua, qui habitare videntur in
                        Vi***; simul et condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Agustaldus">Agustaldo</name></persName> cum uxore,
                        filios et filias suas, vel cum omnia sua; condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Alisso">Alissone</name></persName> cum uxore, filios et
                        filias suas, seu germanos suos, vel cum omnia eorum pertinentia, qui
                        habitare videntur in <placeName key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Baruli</placeName>; condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Bonulus">Boniolo</name></persName> cum uxore, filios et
                        filias suas, vel cum omnia sua, qui habitare videntur ad <orgName>Sanctum
                            Marciano</orgName> in <placeName key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches" ref="#places/2302"
                        >Frecento</placeName>; condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Audoaldus">Audoald</name></persName> cum uxore, filios
                        et filias suas, et cum omnia eorum; condoma nomine <persName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Calvus">Calvo</name></persName> cum uxore, filios et
                        filias, et cum omnia sua, qui habitare videtur in <placeName
                            key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches" ref="#places/2303">Botonto</placeName>; condoma nomine <persName
                                key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><name ref="Ursus">Ursus</name></persName> cum uxore, filiis et
                        filiabus, et cum omnia sua, qui habitat in <placeName key="#Condomae #Agricultural_workers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Remelo</placeName>;
                        simulque et <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >casa</rs> infra hanc <placeName key="#Cities #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches" ref="#places/110"
                            >Beneventanam</placeName> civitatem, qui fuit de <persName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name ref="Radoin"
                            >Radoin</name></persName>, que posita est ad Porta Aurea, et <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >vinea</rs> que posita est ad <orgName>Sancto Vito</orgName> in
                        <placeName key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches" ref="#places/2304">Quinto Decimo</placeName>. Secundum
                        qualiter hec, que supra legitur, in isto Dei loco concessum est a domno
                        sancte memorie <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/2004"
                            >Romoald</persName> socero et avone nostro, et per eius <rs
                            key="#Marquisâ€™/ducal/princely_diploma #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >preceptum</rs> firmatum, sed quia per pravos homines delibata sunt de
                        nominatum preceptum nomina de duas condomas, idest Calbi et Ursi, quem in
                        nostra ostendistis presencia, quem nostra gloria certam agnovimus veritatem,
                        continuo hunc nostrum firmissimum emisimus preceptum, quatenus a modo et
                        deinceps habeatis et possideatis tam vos, qui supra Albileopa, quam et
                        posteras vestras, et nullus ex nostris castaldeis, aut accionariis, vel
                        quisquani homo contra ea, que nostra firmavit potestas, quandoque ire
                        presumat, sed nostra firmitas omni tempore roborata permaneat. Quod vero <rs
                            key="#Marquisâ€™/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum</rs> firmitatis, ex
                        iussione et dictatu supra scripte domne Scaniperge, scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary" ref="Auderissus">Auderissius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. <date>Actum <placeName ref="#places/110"
                                key="#Palatium">Benevento</placeName>, in <rs key="#Cities"
                                >palacium</rs>, mense novembrio, per indiccione octava</date>,
                        feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
